window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Movies often depict grand romances with epic gestures. Like the story of Raj and Simran from <i>DDLJ</i>, or Jack and Rose from <i>Titanic</i>. Many of us yearn to experience such a love. But is it the only kind that exists? </p><p>There’s the excitement of first love, and the depth of long-term relationships. There’s a quiet simplicity in going from friends to lovers and the uncertainty of second chances. Love in its varied manifestations, transforms our life. </p><p>Join a therapist, as he weaves the landscape of love—inspired by the people and the diversity of love he has witnessed in life. Find reflections of your own heart in these characters, who feel like you’ve known them forever. </p><p>Discover how love, in all its shades, connects us all.</p>"; 
